{
  "uid": "tyk-api-troubleshooting",
  "title": "Tyk Gateway - API Troubleshooting",
  "description": "Single-API deep dive: metrics → traces → logs. Progressive disclosure from symptom to root cause. Audience: Backend engineers, SRE on-call.",
  "tags": ["tyk", "api", "troubleshooting", "traces", "logs", "opentelemetry"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource_prometheus",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "label": "Prometheus",
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "datasource_jaeger",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "jaeger",
        "label": "Jaeger",
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "datasource_opensearch",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "grafana-opensearch-datasource",
        "label": "OpenSearch",
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "api_id",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\"}, tyk_api_id)",
        "label": "API",
        "multi": false,
        "includeAll": false,
        "current": {},
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "hide": 0
      },
      {
        "name": "tyk_gw_id",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\"}, tyk_gw_id)",
        "label": "Gateway Node",
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {},
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "hide": 0
      },
      {
        "name": "trace_id",
        "type": "textbox",
        "label": "Trace ID",
        "query": "",
        "current": { "text": "*", "value": "*" },
        "hide": 0
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Troubleshooting Decision Tree",
      "description": "Collapsible guide — start here if you're not sure which row to look at.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 7 },
      "collapsed": false,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Troubleshooting Guide — Start Here\n\n| Symptom | Where to look | What to check |\n|---------|--------------|---------------|\n| **Elevated error rate** | Row 3 (Error Analysis) | Response Flag: `URS` = upstream 5xx → Row 5; `BD` = bad destination → DNS/proxy config; `AUTH` = auth middleware; `RL` = rate limit |\n| **Latency spike** | Row 2 (Latency Attribution) | Gateway latency high → Tyk issue (Go plugin? policy?); Upstream latency high → backend degraded → Row 5 |\n| **Traffic drop, no errors** | Row 1 (check req rate) + Row 6 (Gateway Config) | API count dropped on a node? → deployment issue → use Fleet Health dashboard |\n| **Cache hit rate suddenly low** | Row 1 (Cache Hit Rate stat) | Row 8 Logs → filter `cache_hit=false` → correlate with latency spike time |\n| **Need to inspect a specific failing request** | Row 7 (Traces) | Click slowest/error trace → copy `trace_id` → paste into `$trace_id` variable → Row 8 filters to that request |"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "API Health KPIs",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 7, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Request Rate",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 4, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "5xx Error Rate",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 4, "y": 8, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100 or vector(0)", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100, "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 }, { "color": "red", "value": 5 }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "P95 Total Latency",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 7, "y": 8, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 500 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1000 }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "P95 Gateway Latency",
      "description": "Tyk's own processing overhead for this API.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 10, "y": 8, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(tyk_gateway_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 100 }, { "color": "red", "value": 300 }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "P95 Upstream Latency",
      "description": "This API's backend service latency.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 13, "y": 8, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(tyk_upstream_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 500 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1000 }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Success Rate",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 8, "w": 4, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", http_response_status_code=~\"2..\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100 or vector(0)", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100, "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 90 }, { "color": "green", "value": 99 }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cache Hit Rate",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 20, "y": 8, "w": 4, "h": 4 },
      "targets": [{ "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_requests_with_cache_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", cache_status=\"1\", api_id=\"$api_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(tyk_requests_with_cache_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", api_id=\"$api_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100 or vector(0)", "instant": true }],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none", "textMode": "auto" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100, "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 40 }, { "color": "green", "value": 70 }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 200,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Latency Attribution",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latency Breakdown: Total / Gateway / Upstream (P95 + P50)",
      "description": "The most powerful troubleshooting panel. If gateway latency is flat and upstream spikes, the backend is the culprit — no log diving needed.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 13, "w": 12, "h": 9 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "legendFormat": "Total P95" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by(le)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "legendFormat": "Total P50" },
        { "refId": "C", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(tyk_gateway_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "legendFormat": "Gateway P95" },
        { "refId": "D", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(tyk_upstream_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "legendFormat": "Upstream P95" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 8 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Gateway vs Upstream Latency Share",
      "description": "Visual attribution: what % of total latency is Tyk's processing vs backend? Shifts immediately when upstream degrades.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 13, "w": 6, "h": 9 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_gateway_request_duration_seconds_sum{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_sum{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100", "legendFormat": "Gateway %" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_upstream_request_duration_seconds_sum{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_sum{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100", "legendFormat": "Upstream %" }
      ],
      "options": { "pieType": "pie", "displayLabels": ["percent", "name"], "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "right" } },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Latency Percentile Table",
      "description": "P50 / P95 / P99 × Total / Gateway / Upstream — full picture in one row.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 13, "w": 6, "h": 9 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by(le)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true, "format": "table", "legendFormat": "Total P50" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true, "format": "table", "legendFormat": "Total P95" },
        { "refId": "C", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by(le)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true, "format": "table", "legendFormat": "Total P99" },
        { "refId": "D", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(tyk_gateway_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true, "format": "table", "legendFormat": "GW P95" },
        { "refId": "E", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le)(rate(tyk_upstream_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "instant": true, "format": "table", "legendFormat": "US P95" }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "merge", "options": {} },
        { "id": "organize", "options": { "renameByName": { "Value #A": "Total P50 (ms)", "Value #B": "Total P95 (ms)", "Value #C": "Total P99 (ms)", "Value #D": "Gateway P95 (ms)", "Value #E": "Upstream P95 (ms)" } } }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "P95 Latency by HTTP Method",
      "description": "POST latency 3× GET? Likely a request body processing issue.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 22, "w": 24, "h": 7 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le, http_request_method)(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))) * 1000", "legendFormat": "{{http_request_method}}" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 8 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 300,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Error Analysis",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 29, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate Over Time (5xx + 4xx)",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 30, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100", "legendFormat": "5xx %" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", http_response_status_code=~\"4..\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100", "legendFormat": "4xx %" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Response Flag Distribution",
      "description": "Fastest path to error cause: URS = upstream 5xx, BD = bad destination, RL = rate limited, AUTH = auth failure, KEY = key not found.",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 30, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by(tyk_response_flag)(increase(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__range]))", "legendFormat": "{{tyk_response_flag}}" }
      ],
      "options": { "pieType": "donut", "displayLabels": ["percent", "name"], "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "type": "barchart",
      "title": "Status Code Distribution",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 14, "y": 30, "w": 5, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sort_desc(sum by(http_response_status_code)(increase(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__range])))", "legendFormat": "{{http_response_status_code}}", "instant": true, "format": "table" }
      ],
      "options": { "xField": "http_response_status_code", "orientation": "vertical" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "displayName": "Requests", "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate by Route",
      "description": "Which endpoint is failing — /checkout or /products?",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 19, "y": 30, "w": 5, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by(route)(rate(tyk_requests_by_route_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", response_code=~\"5..\", api_id=\"$api_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{route}}" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate by HTTP Method",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 38, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by(http_request_method)(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{http_request_method}}" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Top Routes by Error Rate",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 38, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "topk(10, sum by(route)(rate(tyk_requests_by_route_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", response_code=~\"5..\", api_id=\"$api_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum by(route)(rate(tyk_requests_by_route_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", api_id=\"$api_id\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100)", "legendFormat": "{{route}}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "options": { "orientation": "horizontal", "displayMode": "gradient", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "color": { "mode": "continuous-RdYlGr" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 400,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Traffic Patterns",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 45, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Request Rate Over Time",
      "description": "Is the error rate spike correlated with a traffic surge?",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 46, "w": 8, "h": 7 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(tyk_api_requests_total{service_name=\"tyk-gateway\", tyk_api_id=\"$api_id\", tyk_gw_id=~\"$tyk_gw_id\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "Total req/s" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Request Rate by Route",
      "datasource": { "uid": "${datasource_prometheus}", "type": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 46, "w": 8, "h": 7 },
